trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> event occurs before the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control navigates to a new document.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>事件發生之前<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>控制項巡覽至新的文件。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can handle this event to cancel navigation before it begins if certain conditions have not been met, for example, when the user has not completely filled out a form.
trans-unit.target: 您可以處理此事件，以符合特定條件未被，比方說，當使用者未完全填寫表單時，如果之前取消巡覽。

trans-unit.source: To do this, set the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property of the WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs object passed to the event handler to `true`.
trans-unit.target: 若要這樣做，請設定<xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs 物件屬性傳遞至事件處理常式`true`。</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also use this object to retrieve the location of the new document through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs.Url%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 您也可以使用此物件來擷取透過新的文件的位置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs.Url%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs.Url%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the new document will be displayed in a Web page frame, you can retrieve the name of the frame through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs.TargetFrameName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 如果新的文件將會顯示在網頁上的畫面，您可以擷取透過框架名稱<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs.TargetFrameName%2A>屬性。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs.TargetFrameName%2A>

trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatingEventArgs"></xref>類別。
